# Intentionally minimal — do NOT add RewriteEngine/RewriteRule here.
#
# The PROJECT-ROOT .htaccess routes every /admin* request through the Laravel
# front controller (../index.php), so this application folder is never served
# directly (that protects .env, vendor, etc. and avoids the /admin -> public
# redirect that caused the stuck loading spinner).
#
# Adding rewrite rules in this file would OVERRIDE the parent rules and break
# that, so it is deliberately left without any.

Options -Indexes
